name: Teichoic acid biosynthesis
name_reaction_str: CDPglycerol + N-Acetyl-beta-D-mannosaminyl-1,4-N-acetyl-D- glucosaminyldiphosphoundecaprenol --> CMP + Teichoic acid

name: Peptidoglycan synthesis
name_reaction_str: H2O + 4.0 ATP + Undecaprenyl-diphospho-N-acetylmuramoyl-(N-acetylglucosamine)-L-alanyl-gamma-D-glutamyl-L-lysyl-D-alanyl-D-alanine + Undecaprenyl-diphospho-N-acetylmuramoyl--N-acetylglucosamine-L-ala-D-glu-meso-2-6-diaminopimeloyl-D-ala-D-ala --> 4.0 ADP + 4.0 Phosphate + 0.5 D-Alanine + Bactoprenyl diphosphate + Peptidoglycan polymer

name: Cell wall biosynthesis
name_reaction_str: 0.05 Teichoic acid + 1.5 Peptidoglycan polymer --> Cell Wall polymer

name: Lipid composition
name_reaction_str: 0.005 Phosphatidylglycerol dioctadecanoyl + 0.005 Phosphatidylglycerophosphate ditetradecanoyl + 0.005 Phosphatidylglycerophosphate dihexadecanoyl + 0.005 Diglucosyl-1,2 dipalmitoylglycerol + 0.005 Diglucosyl-1,2 dimyristoylglycerol + 0.005 Monoglucosyl-1,2 dipalmitoylglycerol + 0.005 Monoglucosyl-1,2 dimyristoylglycerol --> Lipid Pool

name: Cofactor Pool
name_reaction_str: 0.005 ATP + 0.005 NAD + 0.005 NADH + 0.005 NADPH + 0.005 NADP + 0.005 ADP + 0.5 Phosphate + 0.0005 CoA + 0.005 PPi + 0.0005 FAD + 0.005 Acetyl-CoA + 0.005 Mn2+ + 0.005 GDP + 0.005 GTP + 0.005 Ca2+ + 0.005 Cl- + 0.005 Biotin + 0.005 Nicotinamide + 0.005 Co2+ + 0.005 K+ + 0.005 Riboflavin + 0.005 Mg + 0.005 Pyridoxol + 0.005 Thiamin + 0.005 Folate + 0.005 4-Aminobenzoate + 0.005 (R)-Pantothenate + 0.005 Na+ + 0.005 Fe2+ --> Cofactor Pool

name: Biomass Reaction
name_reaction_str: 0.2 Cell Wall polymer + 0.2 Cofactor Pool + 20.0 H2O + 20.0 ATP + 0.05 Lipid Pool + 0.4 Protein biosynthesis + 0.05 DNA replication + 0.15 RNA transcription --> 20.0 ADP + 20.0 Phosphate + Biomass

name: Protein biosynthesis
name_reaction_str: H2O + 20.0 ATP + 0.457 L-Lysyl-tRNA + 0.264 L-Alanyl-tRNA + 0.455 Leucyl-tRNA + 0.16 L-Arginyl-tRNA + 0.12 L-Glutaminyl-tRNA + 0.314 Glycyl-tRNA + 0.135 Methionyl-tRNA + 0.331 L-Seryl-tRNA + 0.328 L-Valyl-tRNA + 0.137 L-Prolyl-tRNA + 0.208 L-Tyrosyl-tRNA + 0.286 L-Aspartyl-tRNA + 0.068 L-Histidyl-tRNA + 0.248 Threonyl-tRNA + 0.062 Cysteinyl-tRNA + 0.498 L-Isoleucyl-tRNA + 0.322 L-Asparagyl-tRNA + 0.219 Phenylalanyl-tRNA + 0.032 L-Tryptophanyl-tRNA + 0.367 L-Glutamyl-tRNA --> 20.0 ADP + 20.0 Phosphate + Protein biosynthesis

name: RNA transcription
